{"tid":440912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[禁室培慾] 主人帶「抑鬱貓」睇醫生 困住5日先知隻貓唔係佢嘅","createTime":"2017-10-19T08:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T11:19:08.000Z","uid":32179,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e460a9a1fb57c7e9abc174bffbe192486efa49","tid":440912,"uid":32179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"黑貓到底是否隻隻都一樣的呢？新西蘭一名貓主就擺了大烏龍，以為自己的寵物貓「行為異常」，帶牠去看獸醫更餵牠吃藥，困了五天後才發現這隻黑貓不是自己的！<br />\n<br />\n電視明星蓋福德（Clarke Gayford）在Twitter分享他朋友的這個搞笑趣事。貓主見寵物黑貓數日來「行為古怪」又變得很惡，於是花了130新西蘭元（728港元）帶貓咪看獸醫。醫生判斷牠可能患抑鬱症，於是開了藥，建議讓貓咪好好休息。<br />\n<br />\n於是貓主把貓咪關在睡房中五天陪玩、陪睡、餵藥，怎料第6天當他走出房間，卻驚見一隻一模一樣的黑貓在客廳出現－－這隻才是他的「正牌主子」！他又想起鄰居其實數天前曾上門查問，是否見過一隻黑貓，他當時答道︰「沒有，抱歉，這兒只有我的貓。」<br />\n<br />\n原來蓋福德朋友的黑貓溜出家玩耍，剛巧鄰居的貓咪卻潛入來，兩隻黑貓「對調」得神不知鬼不覺。這名傻貓主連忙貓歸原主，鄰居數天後通知蓋福德的朋友稱，貓咪被困了數天又吃了抗抑鬱藥，但沒有甚麼後遺症。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而更離奇的是，蓋福德朋友飼養的黑貓是雄性，他鄰居的貓則是雌性，但獸醫竟未發現，蓋福德盡情取笑友人，說「我老友綁架了一隻貓咪，還向牠下藥」。<br />\n<br />\n《新西蘭先驅報》/Twitter<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/19/160320_3b6541657738e1f8bac4fa878961ec8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F19%2F160320_3b6541657738e1f8bac4fa878961ec8d.jpg&h=115b1827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左圖為鄰居的貓咪，右圖為貓主飼養的黑貓(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171018&amp;guid=57342350&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171018%26guid%3D57342350%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=awM1WCYJ6JNa6LRpoiqvWviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ffe59262\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171018%26guid%3D57342350%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=543e1274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171018&amp;guid=57342350&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 逼人食抑鬱藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又真係幾似樣嘅"},{"pid":"52e7d6649d412b419c7187be67fa5eaa3ba946d2","tid":440912,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇相都分到啦，冇忽似樣"},{"pid":"7f4d81465ec308e17c361758e7e1e677043d0a39","tid":440912,"uid":32179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇相都分到啦，冇忽似樣</blockquote><br />\n主人：黑色，應該係我隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1095c125ddbc7f78bc73df3255eda855b27d54e","tid":440912,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇相都分到啦，冇忽似樣</blockquote><br />\n主人：黑色，應該係我隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b0c30199cbdb2d2090b4879b2c8c05869f7b15","tid":440912,"uid":55732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇相都分到啦，冇忽似樣</blockquote><br />\n主人：黑色，應該係我隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMy cat is black<br />\n<br />\nThis cat is black<br />\n<br />\nso, this must be my cat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\